          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>  
  </div>
</div>

<div id="abouts" class="container-fluid m-5 " style="width:85%">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-8 float-start" style="vertical-align: middle;"> 
      <h1>About Us</h1>
      <h2>Photo of me:</h3>
      
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <img src="/static/Horizon Travel.jpg" class="rounded d-block" alt="Horizon Travel Logo" style="float: middle;width:100%">
    </div>
    <main class="container">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="row">
          <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <p>We've been in the business of providing safe and reliable air travel for over 50 years. Our company was founded by a group of aviation enthusiasts who believed that flying should be accessible to everyone, not just the wealthy few.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <div class="row">
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>Our mission is to make air travel safe, affordable, and convenient for everyone. We believe that flying should be a seamless and enjoyable experience, and we're constantly working to improve our services and make our customers' lives easier.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <div class="row">
          <h2>Our Team</h2>
          <p>We have a dedicated team of pilots, flight attendants, and ground staff who are passionate about providing our customers with the best possible experience. Our team is highly trained and committed to safety, and we pride ourselves on our friendly and professional service.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</div>
